<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<subsection xml:id="aa-section-turntable-subsection-k" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Expanding the total derivative of <m>\hat{k}</m></title>

  <p>
    <m>\hat{k}</m> always points out of the screen
    no matter where it is placed in the plane of the turntable or above or below the turntable
    and no matter the angle through which the turntable rotates.
    Therefore,
  </p>

  <p>
    <md xml:id="eqn-total-derivative-k-final" number="yes"> 
        \frac{D \hat{k}}{Dt} = \vec{0}
    </md>
  </p>

</subsection>